description:
Hello guys and gals, it's me Mutahar again! This time we take a look at what appears to be GTA 6 as a playable mod for Vice City with brand new gameplay features and a story crafted by the most obscure modding group I've ever seen... All before a real GTA 6 has actually come out. Thanks for watching!
Like, Comment and Subscribe for more videos!
title: We Got GTA6 Before GTA6...
